          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-copy-3-1715249256321-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped parsley</strong>,<strong> capers</strong>,<strong> garlic </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>sugar</strong> to a<strong> pestle & mortar</strong> and grind to form a paste</p><p>Add a generous drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> with the juice of <strong>half </strong>your <strong>lemon[s]</strong> and mix it all together – this is your <strong>salsa verde</strong></p><p>Tip: Don't have a pestle & mortar? Pulse in a food processor instead!</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
