        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken has had 12 min, remove the smaller pan and<strong> </strong>discard the<strong> </strong>tin foil</p><p>Turn the chicken thighs over and cook for a final 6 min or until cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>brick chicken</strong></p>",
